articles.author: Jamie Barton
articles.title: 16-year-old sensation Gout Gout runs fourth-fastest under-18 100m of all time - CNN
articles.description: Australian teenage sprinting sensation Gout Gout recorded the fourth-fastest under-18 100m time in history on Friday, clocking in at 10.04 seconds at the All-Schools Athletics Championships in Queensland.
